parameters.name: START_DATE
parameters.description: Start date in the format YYDOY where YY is the 2 digit year and DOY is the day-of-year (Jan 1 = 1)

parameters.name: STOP_DATE
parameters.description: Date in the form YYDOY where YY is the 2 digit year and the DOY is the day-of-year (Jan 1 =1).

parameters.name: START_ORBIT
parameters.description: The start orbit number of the 10 orbit record.

parameters.name: STOP_ORBIT
parameters.description: The last orbit of the 10 orbit record.

parameters.name: IPE
parameters.description: 10 values which contain the magnitude of the photoemission current, Ipe (units of 10^9 amps), where each value corresponds to the daily average value. The first of the ten values is the average for the start orbit...
